Author: podimanikee
Title: [Bounty] ICO NOW LIVE ⚡⚡⚡ IP.Gold Bounty Campaign ⚡⚡⚡
Body: IP.Gold maximizes the monetization of services delivered on IP addresses. A proven profitable business model, the IP.Gold Ecosystem takes IP addresses and assigns them to one or more services in our revenue generation lifecycle. The IP.Gold Ecosystem is flexible, allowing for multiple services to be delivered simultaneously on a single IP and a single service to be delivered on a long-term basis, depending on the phase in the lifecycle. This provides short term revenue maximization and long-term revenue stability. The IP.Gold Ecosystem scales easily, so the more IP addresses, the greater the revenue. Best part is, as the IP.Gold is generating revenue on the IP addresses, their asset sale value is increasing.

Author: IPGoldHQ
Title: [Bounty] ICO NOW LIVE ⚡⚡⚡ IP.Gold Bounty Campaign ⚡⚡⚡
Body: IP.Gold Announce Sale To Celebrate Move to NEM Blockchain  IP Gold is kicking off their transfer from the Ethereum blockchain to NEM’s with a generous sale. IP.Gold cites reasons for the transition to long-term sustainability. While Ethereum quickly became the de facto standard for tokens, the number of tokens relying on Ethereum’s infrastructure will continue to put a strain on transaction capabilities and speeds.  Read the details in the article of Coinidol dot com, the world blockchain news outlet: https://coinidol.com/ip-gold-announce-sale-to-celebrate-move-to-nem-blockchain/  https://coinidol.com/upload/resize_cache/iblock/246/900_900_1/246793b1999a9ba60477be21117a37d2.jpg

Title: [Bounty] ICO NOW LIVE ⚡⚡⚡ IP.Gold Bounty Campaign ⚡⚡⚡
Body: The Bounty Camapign Has Been Extended 2 Weeks - Please Check Dates Below   General Rules & Guideline Join the IP.Gold Telegram Room & IP.Gold Bounty Telegram Room. Please, read the following rules carefully and follow IPG Bounty Telegram Room for updates as all announcements and warnings will be made there. IP.Gold Bounty Campaign will last for 12 weeks from 03/28 - 06/19/2018. - **** UPDATED **** We have 130,000 IPG tokens dedicated to the IPG Bounty Campaign. Everyone that participates in the Bounty is going to be required to post an overall update report once a week about their specific bounty activities. Anyone that fails to post a weekly update will not be rewarded with that week’s portion of the stake.  By Participating and signing up for the IP.Gold Bounty Campaign you are agreeing to the IP.Gold Bounty Campaign Terms. HERE  Stake Reward System IPG Bounty Program will use a Stake Issue method to determine how many tokens each individual participant will receive. Each participant will be rewarded a defined amount of stake dependent on activity per bounty. (Total amount of allocated signature campaign IPG tokens / Total amount of all bounty campaign participants' stakes)    Rules and Terms of the Bitcointalk Signature campaign: Join the IP.Gold Telegram Room & IP.Gold Bounty Telegram Room. You must signup and submit a weekly report through the designated links and forms below Only 1 Account per person is allowed. Must be an active account. We are looking for active bitcointalk users. All members need to post at least 5 posts per week having the IP.Gold signature. Posts in alternate cryptocurrencies section are required. Spam, low quality posts and copied posts will not be considered. Add the IP.Gold signature campaign bb-code matching your account rank to the Signature field of your Bitcointalk profile. Deleting your signature/profile picture/personal text will result in your disqualification.  Amount of Stakes by user rank: Hero/Legendary = 6 Stakes per week Sr. Member = 5 Stake per week Full member = 3 Stake per week Member = 2 Stake per week Jr.Member = 1 Stake per week .  Bonuses: +0.5 stakes per week, if you use the IP.Gold avatar + IP.Gold personal text  Avatar https://ip.gold/assets/img/IP_Gold_icon-57x57.png  Personal Text IP.Gold ICO: 5/2/18  Hero/Legendary Member
